<!-- UMA Wandering Traders

Biomes that they spawn in:
forest:		enTraderJen1, enTraderRekt1
desert:		enTraderJen2, enTraderRekt1
snow:		enTraderJen3, enTraderHugh 
burnt:		enTraderJen4, enTraderBob, enTraderJoel1
wasteland:	enTraderJen5, enTraderBob, enTraderJoel1

trader jen has 5 vairations which each match the biome she spawns in:
enTraderJen2 (desert) wears shorts and tanktop, enTraderJen3 (snow) wears sweater and snow hat, enTraderJen4 (burnt forest) wears gloves and fireman's helmet, etc.

enTraderJen1-5	= carries medical supplies
enTraderRekt1	= carries canned food, candy, drinks and seeds
enTraderJoel1 	= carries armor
enTraderHugh	= carries weapons and explosives
enTraderBob		= tools and vehicle parts

all traders also carry general resouces: wood, cloth, coal, duct tape, etc.
